    {
      "id": "PopularPost204681",
      "post_content": "An important thing to keep in mind is the order in which the effects happen.  \n  \nFor example, a creature that is enchanted by [Indestructibility](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Indestructibility) would be destroyed (since enchantments are destroyed before creatures), but an artifact that is enchanted by Indestructibility wouldn't be destroyed (since the enchantment would break after all breakable artifacts were checked).  \n  \nThis makes a lot of interesting things happen.  \n[Aegis Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aegis Angel) would be able to protect just about anything (except for herself), and [Angelic Overseer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angelic Overseer) would die if all the humans on the board were less than 3 CMC (assuming the last two options were picked). [Eldrazi Monument](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eldrazi Monument) dies well before you destroy any creatures, and those pesky creatures enchanted by [Shield of the Oversoul](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of the Oversoul) can have fun eating dirt before they die.  \n  \nArtifact creatures also make things interesting. If there's an [Iron Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Iron Myr) with a divi... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Asmodi0000",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost204681\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">An important thing to keep in mind is the order in which the effects happen.<br/><br/>For example, a creature that is enchanted by <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Indestructibility\">Indestructibility</a> would be destroyed (since enchantments are destroyed before creatures), but an artifact that is enchanted by Indestructibility wouldn't be destroyed (since the enchantment would break after all breakable artifacts were checked).<br/><br/>This makes a lot of interesting things happen.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aegis Angel\">Aegis Angel</a> would be able to protect just about anything (except for herself), and <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angelic Overseer\">Angelic Overseer</a> would die if all the humans on the board were less than 3 CMC (assuming the last two options were picked). <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eldrazi Monument\">Eldrazi Monument</a> dies well before you destroy any creatures, and those pesky creatures enchanted by <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of the Oversoul\">Shield of the Oversoul</a> can have fun eating dirt before they die.<br/><br/>Artifact creatures also make things interesting. If there's an <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Iron Myr\">Iron Myr</a> with a divi... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 204681)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy18984\">Asmodi0000</span>\r\n                                (10/15/2011 8:14:46 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
